features.text:
Enter the track and follow the arrows! Try to avoid the obstacles! 

The timer starts automatically when you cross the checkered stripe and it will reset every time you complete a lap. 

Race around as many times as you like and it will automatically keep track of your fastest lap on the Big Board.

You can reset your "current time" by coming back to the lobby area here and re-enter the track. Or just complete another lap around!

If the timer seems to be acting up you may want to try leaving Voxels and voming back in.
